{"tid":2439307,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港的守墓者 - 陳也","createTime":"2021-03-09T07:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T07:13:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3300fef2391d517acc7d4e9d76eb758f034985","tid":2439307,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T07:13:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210308/BQNCGV6COVBJBP6NTDLVFYKEYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210308%2FBQNCGV6COVBJBP6NTDLVFYKEYY%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy8E4f%2F6cKlXs%2FdqEvpC7bjY%3D&h=5c81ecd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210308%2FBQNCGV6COVBJBP6NTDLVFYKEYY%2F&h=3ed84ed8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210308/BQNCGV6COVBJBP6NTDLVFYKEYY/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港的守墓者 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/udUt-DDHTbUDZrfIQNbwUXpTF1s=/510x374/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Z7TVE5BWHRGBFNEUMTAJMQVXBY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FudUt-DDHTbUDZrfIQNbwUXpTF1s%3D%2F510x374%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZ7TVE5BWHRGBFNEUMTAJMQVXBY.jpg&h=ae019e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立場姐姐陳詞申辯後，單手按欄輕身跨欄回到座位，法院響起掌聲。唔好人比人，老董在兩會紅地毯PK，應景示範田飛龍說的「忠誠廢物」。幾個人又攬又抱，N秒後扶着其他人才勉強站穩。鄭市長在後方齋企，沒施援手，問候一聲就行咗去。你話，時間到底站在哪班人一邊？老董跣過兩鑊，心裏有數。<br />\n<br />\n法院高牆內有畫冇聲，被捕者被迫合演一場六日五夜直踩冇得換戲服的樣板戲，咁係咪令47人好驚呢？看何桂藍朋友帶給她的書，是吳叡人《受困的思想&mdash;&mdash;臺灣重返世界》，就知道高牆內的修煉，正式啟動。以曾服刑人士為教練的團隊「煉冶」負責人彭艾烈發起捐書行動，14天內收到200書目，為在囚者配對，「書送」精神零食。劉頴匡《魔戒》與聖經一齊讀，余慧明睇Dan Brown，有興趣讀《哲學大師寫給每個人的政治思考課》嗎？第二章這樣寫：。。。。。。。。"}]}